snippet.title: Original NESTLÉ® TOLL HOUSE® Chocolate Chip Cookies
snippet.description: This famous classic American cookie is a treat no matter what the age or occasion. Enjoy it with a glass of cold milk.

snippet.title: Crostini Aperitivo
snippet.description: Buon appetito! Add a touch of elegance to any gathering with this tasty Crostini Aperitivo appetizer. Topped with prosciutto and a delicious goat cheese and pesto spread, you've never experienced Tuscany like this before.

snippet.title: Strawberry & Arugula Salad with Cocoa-Spiced Pecans
snippet.description: This elegant Strawberry & Arugula Salad with Cocoa-Spiced Pecans takes a little extra effort but it's worth it. This salad is a perfect choice for entertaining.

snippet.title: Chocolate Chip Cookie Mix In A Jar
snippet.description: A gift of love from your own kitchen.

snippet.title: Baked Ziti With Italian Sausage
snippet.description: Chunky marinara sauce, Italian sausage and mushrooms team up with ziti pasta in this flavorful baked dish. Fennel seeds add a unique Italian flair. This one is perfect for entertaining.

snippet.title: Pumpkin Curry Soup
snippet.description: Curry and white pepper add zest and flavor to this creamy pumpkin soup that is sure to be a fall favorite at your table!

snippet.title: Vegetarian Fajitas
snippet.description: These Vegetarian Fajitas feature a delicious and colorful combination of vegetables. Easy to make too! Serve in tortillas; top with a squeeze of lime juice.

snippet.title: Grilled Fruit with Apple-Maple Syrup
snippet.description: Try this irresistible recipe for Grilled Fruit with Apple-Maple Syrup at your next summer fête. Brushed with a warm blend of apple juice and maple syrup, this grillable dessert is ideal with a scoop of vanilla ice cream. Undeniably delicious, this sweet treat is the perfect summertime indulgence.

snippet.title: Jicama, Mango & Pineapple Salad with Chicken
snippet.description: This colorful Jicama, Mango & Pineapple Salad with Chicken is perfect for entertaining. Featuring thin strips of chicken and seasonal fruits, the secret to this dish is a flavorful coating of chicken bouillon and chili powder – a mouth-watering kick sure to please. Perfect as a starter, main salad or side dish. Chicken may be omitted if using this as a starter or a side.

snippet.title: Apple Quinoa Salad
snippet.description: Packed with nutrition and bursting with flavor, this easy-to-make Apple Quinoa Salad provides a delicious dose of whole grains. And it's the perfect complement to kids' OR adults lunches – boosting energy levels to get through the day. Quinoa is a complete protein, and provides an abundance of nutrition and energy.
